HEADWORD: Purdah
<hw>Pur"dah</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Per. <ets>parda</ets>
a curtain.]</ety> <def>A curtain or screen; also, a cotton fabric in
blue and white stripes, used for curtains.</def>
